title: Boxing with Chris Mannix - Canelo is here
itunes:title: Boxing with Chris Mannix - Canelo is here
description:
Chris talks with Jamel Herring and Jake Donovan about the latest around the world of boxing. Later, Canelo stops by to talk about his upcoming fight with GGG and why it took so long for this rematch to take place. #Herd
